41
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,530
捐献点吧?
For the poor?

42
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,570
你没事吧
Are you troubled,my son?

43
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,810
我想我今天看到了未来
I think I saw the future today.

44
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:45,290
上帝有时是会指引我们 让我们看到我们要走的路
God sometimes gives us glimpses of the path we are traveling.

45
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:48,050
我以前总以为我知道自己要干什么
I always thought I knew just where I was headed.

46
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:49,730
事实上
Truth is,Sister...

47
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:51,810
但我其实是不清楚的
now I'm not so sure.

48
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:53,570
别灰心
Do not despair.

49
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,050
希望在明天嘛
There is always hope.

50
00:02:56,260 --> 00:03:00,490
我不是灰心 我只是不大相信希望这玩意
I don't mean to split hairs,Sister,but I don't believe in hope exactly.

51
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:06,930
我相信的是机会
I prefer to call it chance.

52
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,970
应该抓紧的机会
And a chance has to be grabbed.

53
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,770
你有什么事
What's your problem,my son?

54
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,730
我不是虔诚的基督徒
I'm not a churchgoer,Father.

55
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,570
但我妻子是
The wife's a big fan,though.

56
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:29,010
她让我来一下
She told me to light a candle to Saint Marie of the Incarnation.

57
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:33,290
只要你能帮我 不管什么神佛我都相信
I'll bend the knee to any statue you like.But you have got to help me.

58
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:20,000
飞天大盗 第2季第2集
S02E02 Confessions

59
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,770
Albie.我们很担心你呢
Albie.We were worried.

60
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:37,530
你是我护士啊 这么紧张?我没事啊
What are you,my nurse?I'm fine.

61
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,610
有个好消息跟一个坏消息
Look,there's bad news and there's good news.

62
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:42,130
你没去那 我们丢了那笔生意
When you didn't show,the marks lost their bottle.

63
00:04:42,220 --> 00:04:43,410
那坏消息你们知道了
So you've had the bad,then.

64
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,450
- 你去哪了 - 我们真的很担心你啊
- Where the hell were you? - We were worried.

65
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:48,530
Albie,你要放我们鸽子 也不要在这个时候啊
Albie,if you want to go off-piste,at least let the rest of us know.

66
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:50,850
我也不想那样的
This one has always been a no-no.

67
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:52,490
我也觉得很对不起你们
I've had a bad feeling from the off.

68
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,490
好了好了 那好消息是什么
Okay,so what's the good news?

69
00:04:57,820 --> 00:05:00,330
Keyes.我认识他
Johnny Keyes.Keyes.Oh,yeah.I know him.

70
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:04,090
出生贫民区 是个心狠手辣的人喔
Proper hard man.Proper East End,he is.

71
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:05,240
我还以为他只是个厨师
I thought he was a chef.

72
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:07,970
'"厨房皇帝'" 我老婆有那本书
'"The Kitchen King.'" Yeah,my missus had that book.

73
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:11,130
那就是说你在教堂见到一个很会炒菜的厨子罗
So you saw a fancy chef in a church.

74
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:13,090
不会这么无聊吧
Whoopee diddley doo!

75
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:16,650
不是厨师 我见到的是一个有权有势的人
No.I saw a powerful,arrogant thug.

76
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:21,290
他有钱得要命 可又烦得要死
With cash in his pockets and desperation in his eyes.

77
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:23,250
他烦什么?
What's he got to be desperate about?

78
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:27,090
他出生贫民窟 打家劫舍 白手兴家
He grew up on the streets,robbing houses,talking with his fists.

79
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:29,560
对了 还抢过银行
Yeah,not to mention turning over a couple of banks.

80
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:31,930
不是一两次喔 是很多次啊
And he did time for that.A lot of time.

81
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:35,920
有人说他就该判终身监禁
Some say they should have thrown away the key.

82
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:39,490
那人骨子里就是个恶魔
This man was evil personified.

83
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:44,130
我在监狱里也是跟他们一样
Inside I was just like the rest of them.A nobody.

84
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:48,530
无聊时还不时帮帮厨子打杂
I did kitchen detail just to pass the time at first.

85
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:51,210
后来却真的成了兴趣
But then it got into my blood.

86
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:54,290
我拼命的学习厨艺
And I was devouring books.Hungry to learn.

87
00:05:54,380 --> 00:05:56,010
开始有了些名气
Cooking for the big men.

88
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:59,450
他出狱后买下一家餐馆
So he gets out of prison and buys a restaurant with a bag of gold bullion.

89
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:01,840
- 现在就经营着K's - K's.
- And now of course,he runs K's. - K's.

90
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:04,400
那里现在要订个位子难死了
Who do you have to kill to get a table in there these days?

91
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:12,450
他说是怕我被人杀了
He said it's in case I get a puncture.

92
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:17,090
那他还烦什么
So why is he desperate?

93
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:20,810
很多人都忘了他还有个孩子
What most people have forgotten is the story of James.

94
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,410
叫James的
His son.

95
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:27,330
1974年,他那一岁的孩子被绑架
In 1974,his one- year-old son was kidnapped.

96
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:30,970
之后就再也没有音信了
Never to be heard or seen again.

97
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:33,330
我当时树敌很多
I had a lot of enemies in those days.

98
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,890
我也不知道是谁带走了他
But I'll never know which bastard took him.

99
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:39,370
我付不起赎金 我哪有那么多钱
I couldn't pay what they wanted.I didn't have the ransom,all right?

100
00:06:40,220 --> 00:06:42,410
我得找他
I've got to find him.

101
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:44,010
希望还来得及
Before it's too late.

102
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:45,080
那个Keyes得病了
Keyes is sick.

103
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:49,970
心脏病 说不定哪天自己就挂掉了 当然想找回个继承人
A bum ticker.He wants to find his heir before they stick him in the ground.

104
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:52,570
James现在该32岁了
James would be 32 now.

105
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:55,930
你想找人冒充他儿子
So you're talking birthrights...

106
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:58,690
你就是想这么做吧
inheritance,that's your angle,is it?

107
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:03,170
不好意思打断一下 不过做他孩子还真是可怜
Sorry,but stinging some guy who's still grieving over his long lost son?

108
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:05,770
别同情他
Don't shed one tear for him,my dear.

109
00:07:06,180 --> 00:07:08,210
那人本身就害人不浅了
The guy's a nasty piece of work.

110
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:11,570
我觉得他就在我附近
I got a feeling in my bones that he's close.

111
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:13,000
我会给钱他
I got money for him.

112
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:16,570
让他搞搞生意什么的
Plenty to help him make something of himself,the way I did.

113
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:18,490
如果用钱能补偿他
If I could give him the money...

114
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:21,010
我就给他钱
least then I'd feel I'd done something for him.

115
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,010
那又怎样呢
Now what?

116
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:27,770
我想让他跟他孩子"团聚"
I think we should reunite him with his long lost son.

117
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,210
Albert.
Albert.

118
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:35,130
你今天去教堂干吗?
What the hell were you doing in a church today?

119
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:37,690
今天下午Gil Stewart死了
Gil Stewart died this afternoon.

120
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,530
我一直陪着他
I was there at the end.

121
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:43,050
不是吧 死了?你跟他好得就像两兄弟
Oh,God.I'm so sorry,Albert.You two were like brothers.

122
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:48,210
我们在拉斯维加斯就开始合作
We worked Vegas together.

123
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:50,900
他人好聪明的
That man was made for bright lights.

124
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:52,810
可惜啊
Poor bastard.

125
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:56,170
他在牙科医院 中风死了
Died of a stroke in a dental surgery.

126
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:57,850
我们该起诉那医生
Well,someone should sue them.

127
00:07:57,940 --> 00:08:00,930
他就是那冒牌医生
He was pretending to be the dentist.

128
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:10,010
他死前
Before he died...

129
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:12,130
把这交给我
he gave me this.

130
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:13,440
他的结婚戒指
His wedding ring.

131
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:17,280
做了这么多年骗子
All those years of hard grift...

132
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:20,850
他死的时候却拿着个电动牙刷
and he dies holding a bottle of plaque remover.

133
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:23,410
我要是死了
When I die,Mickey...

134
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:28,410
你得往我口袋塞满钱
I want my pockets to be filled with cash.

135
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:31,010
把Keyes的钱骗到手吧 Michael
Let's take Keyes' money,Michael.

136
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,650
那么
So.

137
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:38,770
给他弄个败家子 你看怎样
How do you feel about playing the prodigal son then?

138
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:41,530
好吧?
Well?

139
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:51,330
Stacie 起起Keyes的老底.
Stacie,find out as much as possible about Keyes'past.

140
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:55,250
越了解他才越能使他相信Danny是他儿子
The details will help convince him that Danny is his son.

141
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:26,810
这些旧新闻是说有个凶悍的匪徒
These old articles talk about a vicious armed robber...

142
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:29,650
勒索 抢劫 无恶不作
into everything from extortion to protection rackets.

143
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:32,730
但他一出狱 洗手不干了
But once Keyes gets out of jail,he reinvents himself.

144
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:35,450
一转眼就成了个厨师
Suddenly he's about as dangerous as Delia Smith.

145
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,770
我想谁也有些事不见得人的
Well,I reckon she's got a dark side.

146
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:39,290
来点三文鱼?
Salmon nibble?

147
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:43,810
有人说他骗了他老朋友的钱
One theory is that he swindled some of his old compadres out of money.

148
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,410
所以那次绑架应该是仇家报复
The kidnap was revenge.

149
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:48,130
好的 那有什么特别
Okay.So how do we usually get a mark?

150
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,770
他们都吝啬的狠
We appeal to their greed.

151
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:52,050
那家伙特意不给赎金的 对吧
This bloke's not looking to make money,is he?

152
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:54,440
他就那样让孩子给人带走算了
He's looking to give it away.

153
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:56,010
我们这次玩玩亲情戏罗
So we spin him a sob story.

154
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,570
那够了吗?
Will that be enough?

155
00:09:57,660 --> 00:10:01,440
咱们要使他心甘情愿给我们送钱啊
You see giving Danny the money has to be his idea.

156
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:10,490
你那是什么
What you got in there?

157
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:12,530
中午吃的肉 看看
Got luncheon meat.Obviously.

158
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:16,090
- 都快坏掉了 - 对啊 我就爱这样的味道
- That's on the turn. - Yeah,that's how I like it.

159
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,450
跟Albert一起的是谁?
Who's Albert with?

160
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:19,610
- 他的新朋友 - 是吗
- His new best friends. - Oh,yeah.

161
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:22,730
是今天早上他碰到的一些的士司机
Yeah,bunch of cab drivers he met this morning.

162
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,210
三个Q
Three jacks.

