00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:32,530
- 好大的牌喔 - 对啊 是很大
- Happens to the best of them. - Yeah.It does.

164
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:35,450
四个皇
Four kings.

165
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:36,730
你输了 老人家
You lose,old-timer.

166
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:40,370
- 再来吗? - 今天不了
- Go again? - Soon.I hope.

167
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:45,130
他赌了好几把了吧
So,he's had a few,then?

168
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:47,210
对啊 来好久了
Yeah.He's been here a while.

169
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:54,850
虎落平原被犬欺啊
A rose in a bed of thorns.

170
00:10:56,460 --> 00:11:00,410
还没干完这事之前不要再赌了
We keep away from blokes on a hot streak unless we got another deck up our sleeve.

171
00:11:02,540 --> 00:11:03,940
Albert?
Albert?

172
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,650
听着 兄弟 你再怎么赌Gil也不会死而复生
Look,mate,gambling's not going to bring Gil back.

173
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:08,530
你打电话给Keyes没?
Have you called Keyes yet?

174
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:17,130
没有 我不想预约 我得跟Keyes谈谈
No,I don't wish to make a reservation.I wish to speak to Mr.Keyes.

175
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:19,210
我是O'Brien神父
Yeah,Father O'Brien.

176
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:23,010
当然不会有像红酒那样香醇的东西
Of course there's nothing like a wine tasting en primeur.

177
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:25,890
我刚从Burgundy回来
I've just come back from a chateau in Burgundy.

178
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:26,960
那真是高级享受
Top stuff.

179
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:31,520
不行
No.

180
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:34,280
当然 这是很浪费的
Of course,it's all bloody show.Still.

181
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:36,010
但我可是嗜酒如命啊
I'm a sucker for the grape.

182
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:37,890
你刚才说你是谁?
Who'd you say you were again?

183
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:39,890
Chris.
Chris.

184
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:43,850
Family Ties是我开的 我们帮人去找回失散得亲人
I run Family Ties.We help reunite estranged families.

185
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:45,730
我一点都不懂得品酒
I don't know anything about wine.

186
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:47,770
这国家只有200人懂得品酒
Only about 200 people in this country do.

187
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:50,370
Sammy厉害得一个顶他们三个
Sammy here accounts for about three of them.

188
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:52,290
是神父叫你来的
So the priest sent you,then?

189
00:11:52,380 --> 00:11:55,570
他三年前就给我们打过电话
He called us about three years ago.

190
00:11:55,660 --> 00:11:57,810
他当时想找自己的家人
Trying to locate his real family.

191
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:02,930
我现在想说是你的儿子 James
I'm talking about James.Your son.

192
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:06,690
我知道很难要你相信 但请听我说
I know this is difficult,but please believe me when I say...

193
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:08,570
不可能
There's no way.

194
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:12,280
神父就打了一个电话 就找到我儿子了?这么简单?
The priest makes one call and finds my son just like that?

195
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:15,730
好吧
All right.

196
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,850
你准备好了就给我电话吧
Call us when you're ready.

197
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,090
你好 是求职中介吗?
Hello,is that Jobseekers?

198
00:12:41,180 --> 00:12:44,530
我想找一批人
Yes,I'm wondering if you could help me.I'm looking for some enthusiastic...

199
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:46,370
要懂得电话礼仪的 要很有热情的
candidates with a very good telephone manner.

200
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:25,930
James三岁开始就开始被不同的人领养
James has been in and out of foster homes since he was three.

201
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:29,050
还被贩卖给一对不能生育的夫妇
He was illegally sold to a childless couple...

202
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:31,490
但是他们后来又改变主意 违弃了他
who had a change of heart and abandoned him.

203
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:34,970
当时应该会有人发现他是你儿子的 但很可惜 没有
He should have been identified as your son,but unfortunately he wasn't.

204
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:38,090
我不相信你们找到他了
I don't buy that you've found him.

205
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:43,770
是他找到 Keyes先生
He found you,Mr.Keyes.

206
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,730
很久前的事了
Quite some time ago.

207
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:49,330
要不是O'Brien神父给我们电话
He didn't know if you'd want to see him.But when Father O'Brien called us...

208
00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:51,090
他才不知道你会不会认他呢
that's when James knew.

209
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,250
我会联系你的
I'll be in touch.

210
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:01,210
我希望这场现场演练能
I hope this brief role-play has given you some idea...

211
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:03,680
让你体会到你将来的工作环境
of the environment you'd be expected to work in.

212
00:14:03,780 --> 00:14:07,450
Starkey先生会给你们发一些面试题目 你们完成它 交好 就可以离开
Mr.Starkey will hand out questionnaires.Please hand them back as you leave.

213
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:10,810
我们会在你们之中挑选两位 一有消息我们就会通知你们
And we'll be in touch with the lucky two we've chosen in due course.

214
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:12,170
非常感谢你们到来
Thank you for your time.

215
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:23,570
那是什么?
What is that?

216
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:28,730
不要打开橱柜看喔
Don't look in the cupboard.

217
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,610
它不会跳出来吓我一跳吧
Is it gonna jump out?

218
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,650
- 上帝啊 - 都告诉你不要了
- Jesus! - I warned you.

219
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:41,650
不然你以为放个空气清新机在这干吗
What do you think the air freshener's are for?

220
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:43,890
Albie.
Albie.

221
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:47,850
葬礼我们就不要去了
Nobody's going to the funeral.

222
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,930
但是Gil会喜欢这的
But,Gil would have loved this.

223
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:52,930
他墓碑上名字写的是Benedict Doonan.
He's being buried under the name of Benedict Doonan.

224
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:55,770
死的时候是冒牌牙医 所以只能用那名
Died a dentist.Buried a dentist.

225
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:59,010
他的墓碑上还不能写自己的名字?
So he doesn't get his own name on his headstone?

226
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:01,730
- 不是吧 - 有什么关系
- Bummer. - What does it matter?

227
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:05,650
会有谁会悼念他?
Who's gonna be there to cry for him?

228
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:12,850
干吗发那么大火
What's eating Gilbert Grape?

229
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:15,530
他不会承认 但是他的确很难过的
Well,he won't admit it,but it's grief.

230
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:20,210
你好,这是Chris
Hello,Chris speaking.

231
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:25,970
好的 完全没问题 我们会安排的
Yeah,no that's no trouble at all.We can get that arranged.Yeah.

232
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:28,890
好的 再见
Okay,cheers.

233
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:34,330
是Keyes的律师
That was Keyes' lawyer.

234
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,210
他们想要做DNA测试
They want a blood test.

235
00:15:45,540 --> 00:15:47,410
快件 医用肝 要送去几楼
Organ courier.Theater.Which floor?

236
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:49,050
你送货清单呢?
Your contact is?

237
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:50,730
清单落在车上了
Contact sheet's back in my panniers.

238
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:51,930
没听说有人要进行移植手术啊
I wasn't told of a transplant.

239
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:54,690
好的 对不起 如果你不要动手术
Yeah,well sorry,love,but seeing as you're not doing the operation...

240
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:57,290
那是不是他们也不要呢?
maybe they didn't make you a priority.Which floor?

241
00:15:57,380 --> 00:16:00,370
- 恐怕我还是不能让你进去 - 好的
- I'm afraid I can't let you through until... - Right.Okay.

242
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:04,160
楼上有个病号 他脸色疮白 就等着这东西
There's a fella upstairs the same color as a canary and he's waiting for one of these.

243
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:08,530
一开始手术 机器一开 就帮他换好肝了
On a slab.On a drip.Cut open.With a little machine doing the job of his liver for him.

244
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:12,240
那你要让他再等我去拿我的清单吗
You want to ask him if he minds hanging on a bit while I go and get my clipboard?

245
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,130
谢谢
Thank you.

246
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:04,090
刚好你来了
Staff.Excellent.

247
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:08,130
我需要在半小时后做血液化验 给我准备一下
I'll need someone available to take a blood sample for me in about half an hour.

248
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:11,920
可以的话
Get me three chairs and an internal phone...

249
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:15,490
还要三张椅子和内线电话 一杯咖啡 放三颗糖
and coffee,three sugars if you can.

250
00:17:16,860 --> 00:17:18,970
我是医生
The doctor...

251
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:20,880
刚上任的
is in.

252
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:28,370
找Dr.Reef的吧 对 他通知过我们了
Dr.Reef.Yes,he phoned to let us know.

253
00:17:28,460 --> 00:17:31,050
- 在第一楼上去 跟着指示牌走就到了 - 好的
- First floor and follow the signs. - Cheers.

254
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:42,130
这很不正常
This is all rather unorthodox.

255
00:17:42,780 --> 00:17:45,210
应该是给你们寄结果的
Protocol is to send these results in the post.

256
00:17:45,620 --> 00:17:48,080
但既然你坚持要现在就知道结果
But since you insist on knowing now.

257
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,450
那就让我看看
Let's have it.

258
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:54,050
我们将你的DNA样本跟James Haworth的对比过
We compared the DNA from your sample to that of James Haworth.

259
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:59,370
结果表明相似度达到99.99%.
The relative chance of paternity is 99.99%.

260
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:02,250
那James....
So James....

261
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:04,450
应该可以确认了
It is as beyond doubt as it can be.

262
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:06,890
是你亲生的Keyes先生
He is your son,Mr.Keyes.

263
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:09,850
我要再找人确认一下
I want a second opinion.

264
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:11,320
什么
I'm sorry?

265
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:13,130
我要有人来再确认一下
I want it reconfirmed.Now.

266
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:17,250
- 你可以看这报告 - 我就要这样做
- Well,you can see the results. - It's the way I do things.

267
00:18:17,340 --> 00:18:19,250
你去找另外一位医生来
You get another doctor in.Now.

268
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:22,490
我不知道能不能麻烦其他医生 大家都很忙的
Well,I'm not sure I can just pull a colleague off the corridor.

269
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,770
如果这样做才能让Keyes放心 那你就这样做好了
If it'll put Mr.Keyes' mind at rest,Doctor.

270
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:30,810
好的
Very well.

271
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:55,650
你要喝点什么吗
Do you want a cup of something?

272
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:58,690
好久了 他搞什么啊 有点不对劲
He's been ages.He's made a cock-up.I knew this wasn't right.

273
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:02,330
对 我想也是
Yeah,think I agree.

274
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:05,090
那 我们就走了?
What,we're going?

275
00:19:05,180 --> 00:19:07,480
我们呆在这也没办法啊
Well,it's not doing you any good pacing up and down here.

276
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:10,250
再说 他们寄给你鉴定报告上就会有再次认可的
Besides,they can always send the second opinion in the post.

277
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:14,120
- 你觉得我们真该就这样走了? - 你决定好了 这是你的问题
- Do you really think we should go? - It's your call.You're in the driving seat.

278
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:17,440
我是帮人家团聚不是拆散人家的
I'm here to unite people not alienate them.

279
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:19,450
再等5分钟好了
Five more minutes.

280
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:21,170
好的
Okay.

281
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,730
这是Mansfield医生
This is Dr.Mansfield.

282
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:30,050
Mansfield我给你看看这化验报告
Dr.Mansfield,I will show you these two DNA results.

283
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:32,250
你来看一下
Your assessment,please.

284
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:37,090
99.99% 相似
99.99% match,Doctor.

285
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:39,330
- 那他们有血缘关系罗 - 对的
- They're related? - Yes.

286
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:42,250
我口好干
I need a drink.

287
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:45,640
做的好
You did very well.

288
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,730
- 那我现在算是个医生罗 - 当然
- So am I a doctor now? - Definitely.

289
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:52,050
那我能帮人动手术吗 我想帮人开刀 做心脏手术 眼部手术 肺部手术
Do I get to do operations?I'd like to operate on a heart,or an eye,or a lung.

290
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:55,920
站稳 站稳啊 吃了那些药是会让人走路都走不稳的
Steady,these pre-meds can really give you the wobbles.

291
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:57,290
还有脑部手术
Or a brain.

292
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:59,130
我带你回你病床好了
Yeah,let's get you back to bed.

293
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,450
我是帮你们而已
God,the things I do for you guys.

294
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,450
- 你漂亮极了 - 对 好看极了
- You look cute. - Yeah,you look fantastic.

295
00:20:04,540 --> 00:20:06,920
他的老婆叫Juliette Keyes.Keyes是她第三任丈夫了
Juliette Keyes.She's on to her third husband.

296
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:08,890
她肯定想要知道你是不是为了钱来的
She'll want to know what you're after financially.

297
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:11,360
那肯定罗 但是不是已经验过DNA了吗?她该相信了吧
Yeah,but the blood test confirms it,doesn't it?I'm his son.

298
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:13,650
不知道 我还是得过来 以防特殊情况
But still,I'll be there to stage-manage.

299
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:16,330
- 你挺漂亮的喔 我们吃顿饭吧 - 开开玩笑而已啊
- Okay,you look great,let's go eat. - Just looking.

300
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,040
谢谢
Thank you.

301
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:26,210
好的 来
It's okay,come on.

302
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:29,210
好的
Right.

303
00:20:33,980 --> 00:20:35,730
这是James
This is James.

304
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:40,250
Jimmy 人人都叫我Jimmy
Jimmy.Everyone calls me Jimmy.

305
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,410
这是Jimmy的未婚妻Paula
And this is Jimmy's missus-to-be,Paula.

306
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:45,930
这地方好漂亮 是吧 Jimmy?
This is an amazing place.Isn't it amazing,Jimmy?

307
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,570
是的 很漂亮
Yeah.It's amazing.

308
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:49,170
我叫Juliette.
I'm Juliette.

309
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:52,010
他这么帅啊 Johnny你说是吧
Handsome devil isn't he,Johnny.

310
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:54,210
是你找上我们的 是吧
So you found us all right,then?

311
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,440
对啊
Yeah.

312
00:20:55,540 --> 00:20:57,410
花了好几年时间了
Well,it took a few years.

313
00:21:01,380 --> 00:21:02,930
最主要的是
The important thing...

314
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:08,530
一开始 不要有什么顾虑 怀疑 什么的
at this very early stage is not to worry about any doubts or fears or anything.

315
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:11,410
大家都要耐心点
Just,you know,be patient.

316
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:18,530
这地方装修不错啊
It's an amazing place,this.

317
00:21:18,620 --> 00:21:20,650
你想在饮食行业立足 就得花点心思
You got to keep ahead in the restaurant game.

318
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:24,810
客人来吃顿饭 你们厨师就得争的头破血流
Customers will eat the food,but when it comes to other chefs,it's dog eat dog.

319
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:27,290
这装修花了我们不少钱啊
Cost us everything,this place.

320
00:21:30,300 --> 00:21:31,690
真厉害
It's amazing.

321
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,450
写菜谱有个窍门 就是要简洁一点
Keep the menus brief,that's the trick.

322
00:21:35,540 --> 00:21:37,370
客人都是想人家来告诉他该吃什么的
People want to be told what to eat.

323
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:39,010
你最拿手做什么菜
So what are you cooking,Jimmy?

324
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:41,090
我现在还刚开始
Well,I'm just at Burger Chef right now.

325
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:44,090
我也有些拿手菜
But I've done stints in some fancy places,ain't I?

326
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:46,810
- 对 - 羊肉 跟苹果塔
- Yeah. - Lamb and apple tatties.

327
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:50,050
我也会做 我做的口味很重的
That's one of mine,with a spicy fig sauce.

328
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:52,570
加点伴菜 烤一下
Saffron,roasties.

329
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:54,570
不要太花俏
You don't want to get too fancy.

330
00:21:54,660 --> 00:21:57,090
如果酱料做的好
Simple food tells its own story...

331
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:59,290
简简单单也会很好吃
providing it's sauced right.Here.

332
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:00,560
试试味
Try that.

333
