吉普赛人的做法
the Catalonian gypsy way of cooking the dish.

671
00:45:01,630 --> 00:45:03,620
特意把鸡
Which is to present the bird...

672
00:45:03,710 --> 00:45:07,710
烤焦
as over-basted.

673
00:45:07,790 --> 00:45:09,430
我把这叫做
That's what I like to call...

674
00:45:10,550 --> 00:45:11,950
乞丐鸡
"Peasant Pheasant."

675
00:45:13,150 --> 00:45:14,740
看上去满好吃的
It looks really good.

676
00:45:16,070 --> 00:45:17,350
我来切
Shall I carve?

677
00:45:26,270 --> 00:45:28,020
试试那酱汁
Try the sauce.

678
00:45:34,750 --> 00:45:36,110
觉得怎样
What do you think's in it?

679
00:45:36,230 --> 00:45:37,820
太浓了
Too much.

680
00:45:44,590 --> 00:45:46,740
好了 要来杯白兰地吗
Right,anyone care for a brandy?

681
00:45:46,830 --> 00:45:47,900
我不要
No,I'm fine.

682
00:45:47,990 --> 00:45:49,060
我要点
Well,I'd love one.

683
00:45:49,150 --> 00:45:50,740
我也要点
Why not?

684
00:45:50,830 --> 00:45:54,140
Johnny 你帮我拿一下吧 就在顶架上
I don't suppose you could reach up to the top shelf could you,Johnny?

685
00:45:59,590 --> 00:46:01,180
没有了
This bottle's empty.

686
00:46:02,230 --> 00:46:05,030
我下去买吧
Well I'll just nip over to the offy then,shall I?

687
00:46:05,110 --> 00:46:06,390
很快就回来
Won't take me five minutes.

688
00:46:06,470 --> 00:46:09,030
Chris 你陪她去吧 一个人去不大好
Lovely,sweetheart,would you go with her,Chris?

689
00:46:09,430 --> 00:46:12,390
好的 没事吧?
Yeah,yes.Is anything wrong?

690
00:46:12,470 --> 00:46:14,030
没事 桌子我们来收就好了
We'll clear the table for you.

691
00:46:17,070 --> 00:46:18,660
你的确跟我很像
There's a lot of me in you.

692
00:46:18,990 --> 00:46:22,750
你有梦想 你也有那个模样 你也有尊严
You got the dreams,and you got the patter,and you got the pride.

693
00:46:23,830 --> 00:46:26,510
但你也跟我一样 很爱吹牛皮
And you got the bullshit.I should know.

694
00:46:27,750 --> 00:46:29,710
我想私底下跟你谈谈
I wanted to say this to you in private.

695
00:46:29,790 --> 00:46:31,940
我尊重你 所以我也坦白跟你说
And I'll do you the honor of speaking plainly.

696
00:46:34,550 --> 00:46:36,070
你还厨艺不行
You ain't got it,son.

697
00:46:36,150 --> 00:46:39,110
你有热情 能凑合弄顿晚餐
You're passionate about your food and you can rustle up a meal.

698
00:46:39,190 --> 00:46:40,630
但你还不行
But you ain't got it.

699
00:46:40,710 --> 00:46:43,510
如果我厨房好一点 工具好一点
If I had a proper kitchen.You know,if I had the right gear.

700
00:46:43,590 --> 00:46:46,500
好厨师就算在旅行车上也能做出好饭菜
A good chef can whip up a gourmet meal on a hot car bonnet.

701
00:46:46,590 --> 00:46:48,790
你做的配料比例都不对
You're slapdash about your ingredients.

702
00:46:48,870 --> 00:46:50,540
太多调味了
You throw too many flavors at it.

703
00:46:50,630 --> 00:46:52,830
调味太多而技巧又不够
Too many ingredients and not enough skill.

704
00:46:55,670 --> 00:46:58,430
我要是还借钱给你
Now,I could throw a load of cash at you anyway.

705
00:46:58,510 --> 00:47:01,030
你也是不会要的
But you wouldn't accept it...

706
00:47:01,390 --> 00:47:03,220
因为你还是很有尊严跟原则的
because you got principles and pride.

707
00:47:03,310 --> 00:47:05,910
我很欣赏你这一点
And I respect that more than you'll ever know.

708
00:47:06,150 --> 00:47:08,030
- Johnny. - 跟我来
- Look,Johnny. - Come with me.

709
00:47:11,550 --> 00:47:13,910
等一下 再给他们5分钟
Hang on.Let's just give them a few more minutes.

710
00:47:20,470 --> 00:47:22,540
你在哪弄到这酒的
Where did you get this Madeira?

711
00:47:24,630 --> 00:47:26,150
在哪弄到的 Jimmy?
Where did you get it,Jimmy?

712
00:47:30,110 --> 00:47:32,070
那天我跟他们回家
You know the day I tracked them down...

713
00:47:32,750 --> 00:47:35,590
我还以为那就是我的亲生父母
those people that I thought were my parents...

714
00:47:36,150 --> 00:47:38,190
他们后来却不让我进屋
they wouldn't even let me in the house.

715
00:47:39,150 --> 00:47:41,460
我才知道他们不要我了
That's when I found out that they'd dumped me.

716
00:47:42,430 --> 00:47:46,190
他们给了赎金 却发现
They paid the kidnappers good money for me,only to realize that I was...

717
00:47:46,470 --> 00:47:48,670
我是你的孩子
your boy.That was it.

718
00:47:50,070 --> 00:47:51,740
就不要我了
They didn't want me anymore.

719
00:47:53,190 --> 00:47:55,230
我那天再去到他们那
I came back that night.

720
00:47:55,790 --> 00:47:57,380
当时我很生气
I was so angry.

721
00:47:58,030 --> 00:47:59,020
之后
So...

722
00:48:02,190 --> 00:48:04,710
我把那地方砸了
I just trashed the place.

723
00:48:06,910 --> 00:48:08,870
那你干吗拿了这酒?
Why did you take the bottle?

724
00:48:10,590 --> 00:48:11,990
因为那狮子
Because of the lion.

725
00:48:18,190 --> 00:48:20,660
我记得我床上挂着的狮子
Lions were my first memory.

726
00:48:21,830 --> 00:48:24,060
可能也是因为那样 我才会那么倔强
Guess that's where I get all my pride from.

727
00:48:28,950 --> 00:48:30,230
Samuel?
Samuel?

728
00:48:31,150 --> 00:48:35,150
这是手制的瓶子 年份是20世纪初的 你看那封口就知道
It's a molded bottle.Early 20th century.You can see the seam.

729
00:48:35,710 --> 00:48:39,630
在这背后还写着 "B 1936 HMS."
Here on the back."B 1936 HMS."

730
00:48:39,710 --> 00:48:44,100
是在1936 Boal vintage的 一个叫H.M.Sortiz的人做的
It's a 1936 Boal vintage produced by H.M.Sortiz.

731
00:48:45,790 --> 00:48:47,020
没开封过
No revenue stamp.

732
00:48:47,630 --> 00:48:48,950
我听不懂
I don't get it.

733
00:48:49,030 --> 00:48:52,100
这软木没有用蜡封住
The stopper cork has no wax cover.But that's not surprising...

734
00:48:52,190 --> 00:48:55,550
所以有些发霉了 还长了些虫子
the cork itself has been infested.Maggots got right into it.

735
00:48:56,510 --> 00:48:59,550
里面的酒都沉淀了
The wine itself is lying low shoulder.

736
00:48:59,830 --> 00:49:00,820
当然不能喝了
It's undrinkable.

737
00:49:00,910 --> 00:49:03,820
但是你也不会打算要去喝这酒
But then,you'd never dream of opening this Madeira.

738
00:49:04,430 --> 00:49:05,470
为什么?
Why not?

739
00:49:05,550 --> 00:49:09,070
这酒是在西班牙封瓶的
This particular vintage was transferred to the Spanish mainland...

740
00:49:09,150 --> 00:49:12,670
可能用运它船来命名这酒
and bottled there.Probably given the name of the ship that brought it.

741
00:49:12,750 --> 00:49:15,060
里昂 就是狮子
Leon.The Lion.

742
00:49:15,550 --> 00:49:19,260
这瓶身有些刮花了
But it's the etching here,in the glass itself.

743
00:49:19,350 --> 00:49:20,990
最厉害的是这了
Now that's amazing.

744
00:49:24,550 --> 00:49:26,220
"F.F."
"F.F."

745
00:49:27,070 --> 00:49:28,060
什么意思
So?

746
00:49:28,150 --> 00:49:31,270
这酒 可是用来献给
What you are holding is a Madeira that was presented...

747
00:49:31,350 --> 00:49:33,660
Francisco Franco将军的
to General Francisco Franco.

748
00:49:33,750 --> 00:49:37,220
在1936年十月
On the day he was made commander-in-chief of the Spanish Army...

749
00:49:37,310 --> 00:49:39,190
他被升为将军的时候送给他的
in October,1936.

750
00:49:39,270 --> 00:49:40,340
"F.F."
"F.F."

751
00:49:40,430 --> 00:49:43,790
这东西是你养父母买来做投资的
Those scum you thought were your parents bought this as an investment.

752
00:49:43,870 --> 00:49:46,510
现在它变成你的了
Now,it's your investment.

753
00:49:46,590 --> 00:49:48,550
那家伙有钱不赎他孩子
This bloke's not looking to make money,is he?

754
00:49:48,630 --> 00:49:50,670
非要让人把他孩子带走
He's looking to give it away.

755
00:49:50,750 --> 00:49:52,310
我们给他来了场亲情戏
So we spin him a sob story.

756
00:49:52,390 --> 00:49:53,790
应该还不够吧
But will that be enough?

757
00:49:53,870 --> 00:49:57,550
要让他心肝情愿给钱给我们
Because giving Danny the money has to be his idea.

758
00:49:57,630 --> 00:50:00,270
我想这会比DNA测试更能说服他的
I mean,that should convince him more than any blood test.

759
00:50:00,350 --> 00:50:02,870
让他自愿借钱我投资
So the son persuades him to invest in a restaurant.

760
00:50:03,550 --> 00:50:06,070
就是说我要去学做菜
That will mean that I got to learn to cook...

761
00:50:06,150 --> 00:50:08,830
那可是太难了
which does sound far too much like hard work.

762
00:50:10,830 --> 00:50:13,350
我们要在其他方面骗到他钱
We need him to pay up in cash.

763
00:50:14,510 --> 00:50:17,790
那 这值好几千吧
So,is it worth a few quid?

764
00:50:19,950 --> 00:50:21,150
对啊
Oh,yeah.

765
00:50:25,590 --> 00:50:28,060
我好久没遇过这种好事了
I ain't felt this ruddy good in years.

766
00:50:28,990 --> 00:50:33,190
你跟Paula该要开始一种新的生活了 我也该帮帮你们了
You and Paula deserve a start in life and you deserve something from me.

767
00:50:33,630 --> 00:50:35,460
作为这么多年的补偿
To make up for not being there for you.

768
00:50:35,550 --> 00:50:37,110
你不想我帮你 好没问题
You don't want handouts.Fine.

769
00:50:37,190 --> 00:50:39,260
我就把这酒买了
I'll buy this bottle of wine off you.

770
00:50:39,830 --> 00:50:41,390
120吧?
Call it 120?

771
00:50:42,390 --> 00:50:45,750
- 120块啊? - 120万
- 120 quid? - 120 grand.

772
00:50:48,190 --> 00:50:50,420
别大惊小怪的 这值这个数
It ain't charity,son.It's what it's worth.

773
00:50:50,510 --> 00:50:53,230
要用来拍卖的话我还能赚一笔
I might even make a slim profit at auction one day.

774
00:50:53,790 --> 00:50:54,780
不是吧
Yeah?

775
00:50:55,230 --> 00:50:57,700
你真给我那么多啊?
So you can give me the money fair and square?

776
00:50:57,790 --> 00:50:58,780
这是生意嘛
It's business.

777
00:51:00,430 --> 00:51:02,550
120万
A hundred and twenty grand?

778
00:51:03,950 --> 00:51:06,710
我以前也见过你这笑容
I've seen that smile on your face once before.

779
00:51:07,550 --> 00:51:09,540
当时你牵着我的小指头
When you first held my little finger.

780
00:51:11,910 --> 00:51:14,550
我们现在才相认还不太晚
It's not too late for me to be a dad to you,is it?

781
00:51:15,350 --> 00:51:17,100
你跟我啊
You and me,boy.

782
00:51:17,630 --> 00:51:18,950
你跟我
You and me.

783
00:51:19,670 --> 00:51:20,660
都是强者
We're kings.

784
00:51:21,030 --> 00:51:22,830
我们是万物之王
Kings of the ruddy jungle.

785
00:51:22,920 --> 00:51:23,950
没错
Yeah.

786
00:51:30,230 --> 00:51:31,220
来
Come on!

787
00:51:35,950 --> 00:51:37,180
Johnny?
Johnny?

788
00:51:38,510 --> 00:51:39,910
怎么回事
What's wrong?

789
00:51:50,190 --> 00:51:51,940
得骗得过老行家
It has to fool a trained eye.

790
00:51:53,390 --> 00:51:55,270
想个法子把这软木瓶盖搞一下
Find a way of rotting the cork.

791
00:51:55,350 --> 00:51:56,710
弄点虫子放进去
Get maggots into it.

792
00:51:56,790 --> 00:51:58,150
用点腐肉就好了
Rancid meat should do it.

793
00:51:59,230 --> 00:52:00,220
把瓶子弄的好像久经风霜的
Age the bottle.

794
00:52:00,950 --> 00:52:03,150
用它来鱼目混珠
An expert will know if it doesn't feel right.

795
00:52:03,910 --> 00:52:06,870
要弄的像真的一样
Every detail has to be perfect.

796
00:52:16,030 --> 00:52:17,590
- 捡回来 - 不要 算了吧
- Get it. - No.Leave it.

797
00:52:18,950 --> 00:52:20,780
- 别让它毁了 - 算了吧
- Save it. - No.Leave it.

798
00:52:32,190 --> 00:52:34,180
我不想死
I don't want to die.

799
00:52:34,270 --> 00:52:36,260
你不会死的 我叫救护车
You're not gonna die.I'm just gonna call an ambulance.

800
00:52:36,350 --> 00:52:38,580
我 我说过好多谎
I've done....I've been....So many lies.

801
00:52:38,670 --> 00:52:40,710
我说过太多了
I've told so many lies.

802
00:52:40,990 --> 00:52:42,900
你都是被逼的 你也不想的嘛
Look,you did what you had to do,didn't you?

803
00:52:42,990 --> 00:52:45,060
你不会明白的 我当时够钱的
You don't understand.I had the money.

804
00:52:45,150 --> 00:52:46,140
什么?
What?

805
00:52:46,230 --> 00:52:48,190
我够钱付赎金的
I had the ransom to pay the kidnappers.

806
00:52:48,270 --> 00:52:49,500
但是我跟他们说 说我没有
But I kept it.

807
00:52:49,590 --> 00:52:53,110
我把钱用来做生意
I called their bluff.It was my money to get started.

808
00:52:53,190 --> 00:52:55,660
我说了谎 之后就失去了你
I took a risk and I lost you.

809
00:52:56,030 --> 00:52:58,230
因为我只想着我的生意
'Cause I wanted the business.

810
00:52:58,670 --> 00:53:00,110
原谅我
Forgive me,son.

811
00:53:00,190 --> 00:53:01,470
我说谎了
I'm a liar...

812
00:53:02,630 --> 00:53:03,700
我骗了你
and a cheat.

813
00:53:03,790 --> 00:53:06,470
原谅我
Forgive me.

814
00:53:06,790 --> 00:53:08,310
我原谅你
I forgive you...

815
00:53:09,230 --> 00:53:10,220
爸
Dad.

816
00:53:33,830 --> 00:53:36,300
这真是精彩极了
It was a work of art,Ash.

817
00:53:36,710 --> 00:53:38,150
你没事吧 Danny?
You all right,Danny?

818
00:53:40,350 --> 00:53:42,340
我知道他是个坏人 还说谎
I know he was a bully and a liar but...

819
00:53:43,950 --> 00:53:46,100
但我也骗了他阿
I lied to him,too,didn't I?

820
00:53:46,550 --> 00:53:49,350
他死的时候听到的都不是真话
The last thing he heard before he died was a lie.

821
00:53:49,550 --> 00:53:51,030
我们不仅仅说谎
We don't just lie to people,Danny.

822
00:53:51,110 --> 00:53:52,990
我们说的都是他们想听的
We tell them what they want to hear.

823
00:53:53,070 --> 00:53:54,270
我们还努力的
And for a moment...

824
00:53:55,150 --> 00:53:56,710
把谎话变得想真的一样
they're truly happy.

825
00:53:57,830 --> 00:54:01,110
好了 让我们看一下 可以吧?
So,can we see it,please?

826
00:54:01,350 --> 00:54:02,750
当然可以
Absolutely.

827
00:54:13,070 --> 00:54:16,060
他用尽力气把这拣回来了
He rescued it,you know.With his last ounce of strength.

828
00:54:17,190 --> 00:54:18,590
他自死也是个强人
He was a strong man.

829
00:54:18,670 --> 00:54:20,470
强人还不是死了?
Weak in other ways.

830
00:54:21,950 --> 00:54:23,910
120万
One hundred and twenty grand.

831
00:54:24,270 --> 00:54:26,470
我给你钱是因为Johnny 想这样做
I'm doing this because it's what Johnny wanted.

832
00:54:26,550 --> 00:54:29,350
- 感谢你所做的一切 - 我也有个条件
- Thanks for everything you've done. - Now this is what I want.

833
00:54:29,430 --> 00:54:30,710
你走吧
I want you to leave.

834
00:54:30,790 --> 00:54:33,350
别再来烦我
Live your happy little lives and don't bother me again.

835
00:54:33,430 --> 00:54:34,910
我还要做生意呢
I've got a business to sell off.

836
00:54:38,230 --> 00:54:40,380
你干吗会做两个?
So why did you bother making a back-up?

837
00:54:43,030 --> 00:54:44,470
以防万一嘛
As a back-up.

838
00:54:53,110 --> 00:54:56,310
对不起 Mickey.我知道我一直让你们难做
I'm sorry,Mickey.I know I haven't been easy.

839
00:54:56,590 --> 00:54:58,310
你朋友死了
You lost a friend,Albert.

840
00:54:58,910 --> 00:55:00,500
伤心可以
It's okay to grieve...

841
00:55:00,870 --> 00:55:02,460
但没必要不理我们
but don't shut us out.

842
00:55:03,110 --> 00:55:05,390
Keyes死了也没什么遗憾的
You know,Keyes died well,didn't he?

843
00:55:06,070 --> 00:55:08,060
他以为他儿子原谅他了嘛
Thinking that his son had forgiven him.

844
00:55:08,590 --> 00:55:11,310
可能Gil死的也没什么遗憾的
Maybe old Gil died well,too.

845
00:55:12,030 --> 00:55:13,430
都完成自己的心愿了
Doing what he loved.

846
00:55:15,030 --> 00:55:17,750
我不知道 可能我想太多了
I don't know,maybe I worry too much.

847
00:55:18,230 --> 00:55:21,110
生命是没终点的
There is no destination in life.

848
00:55:21,190 --> 00:55:23,310
过程才是最重要的
The journey is everything.

849
00:55:24,990 --> 00:55:26,140
什么?
What?

850
00:55:27,190 --> 00:55:31,150
你有时候
It's just,the things you come out with sometimes,Albert.

851
00:55:31,830 --> 00:55:33,870
你还蛮给我们鼓励的
You're still an inspiration,you know that?

852
00:55:34,590 --> 00:55:35,790
像老爸一样?
Father figure?

853
00:55:35,870 --> 00:55:40,500
我想是像爷爷一样吧 好了 谈一下guru吧
I was thinking more grandfather figure.Okay,what about guru?

854
00:55:41,510 --> 00:55:43,390
guru 好的
Now guru,I like.

855
00:55:47,030 --> 00:55:48,910
没什么好怕的
And there's nothing to be scared of.

856
00:55:49,630 --> 00:55:52,390
我们不是还在一起嘛
